1. *Ostaju* mi samo ruže kao uspomena. (Only roses *remain* as a memory for me.)
2. Kada *ostaju* sami kod kuće, deca vole da prave nered. (When they are left alone at home, children like to make a mess.)
3. Često se pitam šta *ostaje* od naših snova nakon što ih ostvarimo. (I often wonder what *remains* of our dreams after we achieve them.)
4. Nekad su *ostajali* do kasno u noć i pričali o svemu i svačemu. (They used to *stay* up late and talk about everything and anything.)
5. *Ostajemo* bez vremena, moramo da požurimo. (We are *running out* of time, we have to hurry up.)
6. Oni su *ostali* u gradu, a mi smo se vratili kući. (They *stayed* in the city, and we went back home.)
7. Kada bih mogla da *ostavim* sve obaveze i odem negde daleko... (If I could *leave* all my obligations and go somewhere far away...)
8. *Ostavila* sam svoj telefon kod kuće i sad ne mogu da se javim. (I *left* my phone at home, and now I can't answer it.)
9. Bez obzira na sve, oni *ostaju* najbolji prijatelji. (Regardless of everything, they *remain* the best friends.)
10. *Ostavljam* ti poruku da se vidimo sutra. (I'm *leaving* you a message to meet tomorrow.)